the pilot and crew were considered experienced and are assigned 
to the 183rd aviation attack helicopter battalion the missing 
helicopter is a uh1h huey a vietnamera aircraft about 20 
years old 
gollaher said there is no history of unusual mechanical problems 
with the missing aircraft the names of the crew members were not 
released 
