a scandinavian airlines system plane 
returning from greece lost part of its tail while landing at 
stockholms international airport but no one was hurt an sas 
spokesman said sunday 
the md82 a modernized dc9 was arriving at arlanda airport 
from athens with 156 passengers aboard when the incident occurred 
saturday night 
